name: Snowman Christmas Hair Bow
description:
Topped with a cute snowman and featuring glittery red and green snowflakes and fun polka dots, this large bow is perfect for the Christmas season!

DETAILS
-measures approximately 4.5"
-attached to an alligator clip
-three layers of grosgrain ribbon
-ribbons are heat sealed to prevent fraying

name: Pink Gingham Crown Bow
description:
Made with layers and layers of woven and grosgrain ribbon, this boutique style bow is finished with a sequined crown center!

DETAILS
-securely attached to an alligator clip
-measures approximately 4.5" across
-ribbons are heat sealed to prevent fraying

name: Miss Priss Hair Bow Holder
description:
This large bow holder is made of painted wood with sparkly lettering and lots of fun polka dots. Grosgrain ribbon is securely attached and ready for you to clip on your bows!

DETAILS
-backed with a picture hanger, so all you need to hang it is a nail!
-will hold between 30-60 bows

name: Little Ballerina Hair Bow Holder
description:
This cute ballerina bow holder is made of painted wood and mini rhinestones. Grosgrain ribbon is securely attached and ready for you to clip on your bows!

DETAILS
-backed with a picture hanger, so all you need to hang it is a nail!
-will hold between 15-30 bows
